modDescription:
This is just a simple modlet that adds 34 blocks with an assortment of [textures](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-textures/) and more.

New Decorative Blocks will be added to this on a regular basis.

**Recently Added:**

Bushes!

Textured blocks have 2500 health. Not upgradeable and not paintable. Only shape is cube!

Since adding paint textures is not really an option this is about best we can get.

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/13TgsTunCsINUCDUHvspiYvnUqrGnct6K/view?usp=sharing)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/23986-age-of-oblivion-all-modlets-oblivion-mods/).

**Credits:** [Pipermac](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/pipermac/)
